{"tid":1464190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攬炒？我屌你老母啦","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:07:07.000Z","uid":158559,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d7deb9998ed430a4edaefbbcf2eb83560b95f4e7","tid":1464190,"uid":158559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:34:44.000Z","msg":"如果真係攬炒，全香港一齊失業一齊食屎，你接唔接受到？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460484</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今朝上面呢個post成萬個正皮話支持攬炒<br />\n一到夜晚死班撚樣轉哂風向話國際同外國旅客感覺會好撚差㗎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想問咁又點呀？</span></span><br />\n你地咁有潔癖不如唔撚好抗爭啦<br />\n顧完香港人民意仲要理撚埋外國人民意？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家我哋係要攬炒呀</span></span><br />\n我哋而家自己人都顧唔掂你走去顧外國人？<br />\n係唔撚係忽撚咗呀？<br />\n<br />\n旅客返唔到去咪唔好再嚟香港囉<br />\n國際覺得香港唔安全咪發旅遊警示囉<br />\n甚至乎外商驚咗咪撤資囉<br />\n香港變成咁錯不在我哋呀<br />\n<br />\n到今日你覺得仲有底線 <br />\n行動仲要得到滿足所有人 乜都要好好睇睇嘅<br />\n唔該你好好反省吓咁唔對得住呢場運動開始到而家所犧牲自己前途甚至生命嘅手足"},{"pid":"3efd5332587aa18cc92a4e637e35628da679ecbd","tid":1464190,"uid":203701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:40:20.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"31cfceec6e1a929d84a3e3bb68f61930035778fc","tid":1464190,"uid":28597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:56:12.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割席"},{"pid":"3d6fa3221d303a179ed8cd9d9f152a8156e4d863","tid":1464190,"uid":291486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"787e7b2954f7bc7b65a7d43c8ff863cf6182ac9b","tid":1464190,"uid":158559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31cfceec6e1a929d84a3e3bb68f61930035778fc","tid":1464190,"uid":28597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:56:12.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割席"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:04:24.000Z","msg":"分你老母化 國難當前  <br />